          "INSTITUTE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "1USAPPO"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Phillips Petroleum Company, Atomic Energy",
                "Division, Idaho Falls, Idaho."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "REAC"
                ],
                "institute": "1USAINL"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The Reactivity Measurements Facility",
                " (RMF) is a low power reactor located in the fuel",
                "element storage canal of the Material Testing Reactor",
                "at the National Reactor Testing Station in Idaho."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The correction to eta was introduced to obtained the",
                "Maxwellian-averaged eta ratio. This factor",
                "[(sigma/sigma m)U-233/((sigma/sigma m)U-235)]*",
                "[1-((sigma ef flux e)/(sigma f flux))U- 33]/",
                "[1-((sigma ef flux e)/(sigma f flux))U-235] where",
                "subscripts m, e and f denote, respectively,",
                "Maxwellian, above Maxwellian and fission, and sigma",
                "the effective microscopic cross section for the",
                "indicated energy region."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "REAC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The RMF measurements were made on 46-ml",
                "samples sealed in polyethylene capsules. Dilutions of",
                "the 1-N HNO3 solutions permitted extrapolation of the",
                "differential reactivity to infinite dilution to",
                "determine corrections for self-shielding. The three",
                "experimental positions of the RMF used represent a",
                "range of flux spectra of equivalent thin 1/v-",
                "cadmium ratios from 28 to 150."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " No details on sources of uncertainties."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The measurements were corrected for all known sample",
                "impurity effects."
              ]
            }
          ],
